Disease:     HIV/AIDS
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    HIV
Transmission:Sexual contact, blood
Symptoms:    Flu-like; then AIDS symptoms
Treatment:   Antiretroviral therapy (ART)
Deaths/yr:   0.65M
Vaccine:     No (in development)
Discovered:  1983

Disease:     Polio
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    Poliovirus
Transmission:Fecal-oral
Symptoms:    Paralysis in severe cases
Treatment:   No cure; supportive care
Deaths/yr:   0M
Vaccine:     Yes (near-eradicated)
Discovered:  1840

